thread.title: brams kahoon
thread.title_full: Trade Tested reviewed by brams kahoon

author: brams kahoon
title: brams kahoon
text:
I recently purchase a 26cc blower vac,was impress by the prompt delivery,upon inspection I was impress with the quality for the price.started up just a few easy tugs and wow it blows.
Also tried the vac function,easy to put together,no need to be a pro to put it together,sucks the leaves and shreds it to fine bits,I even checked the shredding blades after a few minutes use,it was clean.
Very fuel efficient
Overall very good product five stars from me.
